Is there any value of &lt;math> k &lt;/math> for which the function &lt;math> f &lt;/math> below is a probability density function?

&lt;math>
 f(x) =
 \begin{cases}
 \frac{2k}{(k+x)(k-x)} &amp; \text{for } 0 \leq x \leq \frac{k}{2} \\
 0 &amp; \text{otherwise.}
 \end{cases}
&lt;/math>

If yes, find all such values of &lt;math> k. &lt;/math> If there is no such &lt;math> k &lt;/math>, explain why.
